        'Let\'s get specific, because this can stay beautifully abstract in a way that feels true but changes nothing.',
        'Think about your primary practice environment right now. The place, the conditions, the format, the people involved or absent, the tools you use, the feedback mechanisms that exist, the stakes attached to performance, the timing of your sessions. The totality of the context in which you do the thing you\'re trying to get better at.',
