        'Here is something subtle that most people miss when they first encounter affordance theory.',
        'Affordances change as you change.',
        'The same environment offers completely different things to different people at different levels of skill. This is not metaphorical. It is a precise description of how perception works, and it has major implications for how you think about your practice environment.',
